---
title: Cheesy Beef, Mushroom & Filo Pastry Pie with Avocado & Balsamic Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs in a veggie and mushroom loaded beef base that's full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with a light
and flakey filo pastry. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for an optimally crisp pastry!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-beef-filo-pastry-pie-ada95043.jpg
